{"type":"message","id":"6294f940","parentId":"c8453991","timestamp":"2026-04-28T06:05:00.846Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Gmail has no new emails in the last hour. iCloud has 4 emails but they are all marked as read (R flag) except one that has \"!\" flag. Let me check the himalaya timestamps more carefully.\n\nLooking at the iCloud emails:\n- ID 9: No flags - from RC Leasing, \"Re: Looking for new apartment\" - 2026-04-27 19:06\n- ID 8: ! R flags - from RC Leasing, \"Re: Looking for new apartment\" - 2026-04-27 12:20\n- ID 7: R flag - from RC Leasing, \"Re: Looking for new apartment\" - 2026-04-13\n\n\n- ID 6: R flag - from Taylor Alexander, \"Re: Apartment Inquiry (Around mid June)\" - 2026-01-22\n\nSince the last email check was an hour ago and these iCloud messages are dated today or months back, they're likely already seen. I need to figure out what \"newer_than:1h\" actually means for himalaya to determine if any of these qualify as new.\n\nThe cron job just says \"Check emails\" without specifying a timeframe, so I'm not sure if it means since the last check or within the past hour. Looking at the timestamps more carefully—ID 9 came in at 19:06 UTC today and ID 8 at 12:20 UTC today, both relatively recent. Since the task asks me to report new iCloud emails, I should probably read through these to see what's actually there and determine if they're genuinely new based on whatever the baseline is. Looking at the timestamps more carefully, ID 9 from today at 19:06 UTC could be unread if it came in after the last check, while the others are older. The \"!\" flag on ID 8 indicates it's urgent or flagged, so I should read through these messages to give Bobby a complete picture of what's new across both accounts.","thinkingSignature":"b1314a37c41b11577bbc5b3feb5eb5e839fa1752331d77bf62f503cdf7a89592"},{"type":"text","text":"Gmail has no new emails. Let me check the iCloud emails more closely — ID 9 has no flags and is from today.\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_4kuwucht22zg_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"himalaya message read 9 --account icloud 2>&1"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":957,"output":480,"cacheRead":19036,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20473,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777356285565,"responseId":"063f80fdfe57a14f6917031def540448"}}
{"type":"message","id":"91dfd093","parentId":"6294f940","timestamp":"2026-04-28T06:05:02.053Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_4kuwucht22zg_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[2m2026-04-28T06:05:01.667694Z[0m [33m WARN[0m [2mimap_codec::response[0m[2m:[0m Rectified missing `text` to \"...\"\n[2m2026-04-28T06:05:01.668270Z[0m [33m WARN[0m [2mimap_codec::response[0m[2m:[0m Rectified missing `text` to \"...\"\n[2m2026-04-28T06:05:01.668295Z[0m [33m WARN[0m [2mimap_codec::response[0m[2m:[0m Rectified missing `text` to \"...\"\n[2m2026-04-28T06:05:01.668337Z[0m [33m WARN[0m [2mimap_codec::response[0m[2m:[0m Rectified missing `text` to \"...\"\nFrom: RC Leasing <RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\nTo: rtg.bobby@icloud.com <rtg.bobby@icloud.com>\nSubject: Re: Looking for new apartment\n\nHello,\n\nOk sounds good. I may have one for that time frame. Just keep in mind they are first come first serve. Once approved, your application stays with us until we can link you to a unit. Once Logan is done, we can begin the process. Any questions feel free to reach out.\n\n\nAmy Smith\n\nLeasing Agent\n\nT  |  845.452.3450 x312\nE  |  RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com<mailto:RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\n\nW | royalcoveapts.com\n\n\n\n[A picture containing text, font, screenshot, graphics  Description automatically generated]\n\n\n\n________________________________\nFrom: rtg.bobby@icloud.com <rtg.bobby@icloud.com>\nSent: Monday, April 27, 2026 12:17 PM\nTo: RC Leasing <RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\nSubject: Re: Looking for new apartment\n\nGood afternoon, We were hoping sometime before June 4th. I will follow up once Logan completes his portion of the application. Thank you, Robert Galletta                                              \nReport This Email<removed-link>\n\nGood afternoon,\n\nWe were hoping sometime before June 4th.\nI will follow up once Logan completes his portion of the application.\n\nThank you,\nRobert Galletta\n\n\nOn Apr 27, 2026, at 8:20 AM, RC Leasing <RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com<mailto:RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>> wrote:\n\n\nGood Morning,\n\nOnce Logan completes his, I can run the apps. When are you looking to move by so I can make sure I will have one Available?\n\n\nAmy Smith\n\nLeasing Agent\n\nT  |  845.452.3450 x312\nE  |  RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com<mailto:RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\n\nW | royalcoveapts.com<https://shared.outlook.inky.com/link?domain=royalcoveapts.com&t=h.eJxNjkEOwiAURK_SsLalQAXbVa8Cnx9sRD-h1NgY764sNG7nzeTNk205sqlh51LSxHmm3UagO9pU1g7oyg4Nu9RCxMdyC4VubcqUMJe9DZm2xDNEtOuHzb9KCnXKHYAAiSNqZ3EEpb0dBiHtUSqPPUoujDGq19qMXX8SRktVdVh1uYTOkXP7vECkzX-_-Ar_otcb3UI-gg.MEUCIQCrAoq9O9zx8X-WiCWAUINSyTP-_NOMlxkZwbLwiSoYkQIgeBorTOa8cgxlkQb1ARuodw22Fxfr2BJ6_Md9GJYWmkA>\n\n\n\n<Outlook-A picture .png>\n\n\n\n________________________________\nFrom: rtg.bobby@icloud.com<mailto:rtg.bobby@icloud.com> <rtg.bobby@icloud.com<mailto:rtg.bobby@icloud.com>>\nSent: Saturday, April 25, 2026 1:49 PM\nTo: RC Leasing <RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com<mailto:RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>>\nSubject: Re: Looking for new apartment\n\n\nHi Amy,\n\n\n\nI wanted to reach out to let you know that I have completed and submitted my portion of the rental application for Royal Cove. I am currently waiting on my partner, Logan, to finish his part of the application on his end.\n\n\n\nWe are still very interested in a 1 bedroom / 1 bathroom unit. Please let me know if you need anything else from me in the meantime, or if there are any updates on availability.\n\n\n\nThank you,\n\nRobert Galletta\n<#part type=image/png filename=\"/Users/bobbygalletta/Downloads/Outlook-A picture .png\"><#/part>"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1196,"aggregated":"[2m2026-04-28T06:05:01.667694Z[0m [33m WARN[0m [2mimap_codec::response[0m[2m:[0m Rectified missing `text` to \"...\"\n[2m2026-04-28T06:05:01.668270Z[0m [33m WARN[0m [2mimap_codec::response[0m[2m:[0m Rectified missing `text` to \"...\"\n[2m2026-04-28T06:05:01.668295Z[0m [33m WARN[0m [2mimap_codec::response[0m[2m:[0m Rectified missing `text` to \"...\"\n[2m2026-04-28T06:05:01.668337Z[0m [33m WARN[0m [2mimap_codec::response[0m[2m:[0m Rectified missing `text` to \"...\"\nFrom: RC Leasing <RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\nTo: rtg.bobby@icloud.com <rtg.bobby@icloud.com>\nSubject: Re: Looking for new apartment\n\nHello,\n\nOk sounds good. I may have one for that time frame. Just keep in mind they are first come first serve. Once approved, your application stays with us until we can link you to a unit. Once Logan is done, we can begin the process. Any questions feel free to reach out.\n\n\nAmy Smith\n\nLeasing Agent\n\nT  |  845.452.3450 x312\nE  |  RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com<mailto:RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\n\nW | royalcoveapts.com\n\n\n\n[A picture containing text, font, screenshot, graphics  Description automatically generated]\n\n\n\n________________________________\nFrom: rtg.bobby@icloud.com <rtg.bobby@icloud.com>\nSent: Monday, April 27, 2026 12:17 PM\nTo: RC Leasing <RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\nSubject: Re: Looking for new apartment\n\nGood afternoon, We were hoping sometime before June 4th. I will follow up once Logan completes his portion of the application. Thank you, Robert Galletta                                              \nReport This Email<removed-link>\n\nGood afternoon,\n\nWe were hoping sometime before June 4th.\nI will follow up once Logan completes his portion of the application.\n\nThank you,\nRobert Galletta\n\n\nOn Apr 27, 2026, at 8:20 AM, RC Leasing <RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com<mailto:RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>> wrote:\n\n\nGood Morning,\n\nOnce Logan completes his, I can run the apps. When are you looking to move by so I can make sure I will have one Available?\n\n\nAmy Smith\n\nLeasing Agent\n\nT  |  845.452.3450 x312\nE  |  RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com<mailto:RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\n\nW | royalcoveapts.com<https://shared.outlook.inky.com/link?domain=royalcoveapts.com&t=h.eJxNjkEOwiAURK_SsLalQAXbVa8Cnx9sRD-h1NgY